<InfoCard>
    <InfoHeading TextPadding="Padding.Is4.OnY">GENERAL INFORMATION</InfoHeading>

    <InfoList>
        <InfoListItem>
            The tournament will be held on <b>August 2-4 at the Atlas Tube Centre</b> (447 Renaud Line Rd.)
        </InfoListItem>
        <InfoListItem>
            There is a <b>$50 registration fee</b>. This fee covers ice, refs, timekeepers and prizes
        </InfoListItem>
        <InfoListItem>
            Each team is <b>guaranteed four games</b>
        </InfoListItem>
        <InfoListItem>
            There will be <b>four teams</b>, each with an assigned team captain
        </InfoListItem>
        <InfoListItem>
            Teams will be drafted by their respective captains. <b>Players must be registered prior to the draft
                (July 25) in order to play</b>
        </InfoListItem>
        <InfoListItem>
            There will be prizes awarded to the winning teams
        </InfoListItem>
    </InfoList>
</InfoCard>

<br>

<InfoCard>
    <InfoHeading TextPadding="Padding.Is4.OnY">GAME INFORMATION</InfoHeading>

    <InfoList>
        <InfoListItem>
            Each game will start with a <b>3-minute warmup</b> and will have <b>three 10-minute stop-time
                periods</b>.
        </InfoListItem>
        <InfoListItem>
            Game rules will follow similar structure to that of OHA with the exception of fighting, which will result
            in 5-minute majors to both participants
        </InfoListItem>
        <InfoListItem>
            Stats will be tracked. They will be posted and available to view after each game
        </InfoListItem>
        <InfoListItem>
            The first three games are round-robin. Teams will be seeded based on their records. If teams finish with
            the same records, the tie-breaker will be determined in the following order
            <OrderedList>
                <OrderedListItem>
                    Head-to-head result
                </OrderedListItem>
                <OrderedListItem>
                    Goal differential
                </OrderedListItem>
                <OrderedListItem>
                    Goals scored
                </OrderedListItem>
            </OrderedList>
    </InfoList>
</InfoCard>

<br>

<InfoCard>
    <InfoHeading TextPadding="Padding.Is4.OnY">REGISTRATION</InfoHeading>

    <InfoList>
        <InfoListItem>
            To register, click <b>REGISTER</b> on the top menu bar
        </InfoListItem>
        <InfoListItem>
            You will be redirected to a payment page where you can pay for your registration fee
        </InfoListItem>
        <InfoListItem>
            Upon completion, you will be redirected to an information form
        </InfoListItem>
        <InfoListItem>
            If you do not wish to pay online, you can pay via Interac e-Transfer to <b>nicbolton17@icloud.com</b>. You
            will
            receive a link to a registration form following payment
        </InfoListItem>
    </InfoList>
</InfoCard>